🎬 Expansion Concept

From Restoration → Probabilistic Reconstruction

Two modes (keep them separate)

1. Restoration (what we already covered)
	•	film exists
	•	you enhance signal

2. Reconstruction (what you’re describing)
	•	no visuals exist (or incomplete)
	•	you generate from text + context

👉 This is a different product:

historically-informed cinematic generation

⸻

🧠 Core Engine

“Text → World → Film”

source text
→ semantic parse
→ world model
→ character + environment inference
→ scene construction
→ rendering


